### Performance Comparison

| Test Operation | Mesh Tube | Document DB | Comparison |
|----------------|-----------|-------------|------------|
| Time Slice Query | 0.000000s | 0.000000s | Comparable |
| Compute State | 0.000000s | 0.000000s | Comparable |
